# VHS Demo — darknet-mcp-server
Output .github/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

# List all tools
Type `npx darknet-mcp-server --list`
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

# Check Tor status
Type `npx darknet-mcp-server --check-tor`
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Help
Type `npx darknet-mcp-server --help`
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Sleep 3s
